metadata.name: Trust
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 7 video, that have been issued as a single, unique edition.

Video_1080x1080 px

The most important thing in a relationship between a man and a woman is to trust each other.

This video captures the essence of that feeling.

The owner of this video will be a lucky man, he is sure to meet a man who will trust in life!

My video is charged with the magic that will happen in your life!!!
